216
00:10:43,425 --> 00:10:44,075
Ayahanda.

217
00:10:44,075 --> 00:10:46,000
Walaupun awak tak tangkap Lin Tanhua

218
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,039
tapi awak perlu dengar apa yang
Xu Fengnian mahu cakap.

219
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:49,519
Lagipun, dia mewakili Liang Utara.

220
00:10:51,125 --> 00:10:52,080
Kalau tak pergi jumpa dia.

221
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,639
Maka tangkap orang dulu.

222
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:54,879
Jangan pedulikan dia.

223
